{"word":"G3562 - νουνεχῶς - nounechōs - noon-ekh-oce' - Discreetly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">νουνεχῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">nounechōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">noon-ekh-oce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Discreetly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"விவேகமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"wisely, prudently, discreetly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from a compound of the accusative of <a href=\"#/G3563 - νοῦς - noûs - nooce/3563\">G3563</a> and <a href=\"#/G2192 - ἔχω - échō - ekh'-o/2192\">G2192</a>; in a <i>mind having</i> way, that is, <i>prudently:</i> - discreetly.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3562/3562\">G3562</a>, <a href=\"#/G3563/3563\">G3563</a>"}]}